text: Teal can mean many things, such as: * A type of duck, ** Ringed teal,Callonetta leucophrys ** Common teal, Anas crecca ** Green-winged teal, Anas carolinensis ** Black teal, Aythya novaeseelandiae ** Brown teal, Anas aucklandica ** Silver teal, Anas versicolor ** Cape teal, Anas capensis ** Marbled teal, Marmaronetta angustirostris ** Blue-winged teal, Anas discors * Teal (color), a bluish green color * Claud Eustace Teal (a.k.a. Mr. Teal), a person seen in the books of Leslie Charteris
title: Teal
